@port = 5236
@host = http://localhost:{{port}}

### 1. Request SysAdmin Cryptographic Token
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999",
  "role": "SysAdmin"
}

### Extraction Variable (Corrected to lowercase 'token' to match System.Text.Json serialization)
@authToken = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 2. Execute Secured Transfer (Reverse Flow)
POST {{host}}/api/transactions/transfer
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
X-Idempotency-Key: 97698999-9998-9999-9999-999999999999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceAccountId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
  "destinationAccountId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### 3. Provision a New Agent Account (Requires SysAdmin Token)
POST {{host}}/api/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountType": "AgentFloat",
  "kycTier": "Tier3"
}

### 4. Audit the Derived Balance
GET {{host}}/api/accounts/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 5. Audit the Derived Balance
GET {{host}}/api/accounts/22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}